    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Clan</p><p>Prerequisite: Kashu Clan, Level 8+</p><p>You harness your dark chakra to enhance the power of your clan's Hijutsu. You gain the following benefits;</p><p>• Increase your Intelligence or Wisdom score by +1, to a maximum of 20</p><p>• When a jutsu you cast would benefit from your Reckless Genjutsu clan feature and requires an attack roll, you also increase the critical threat range by the same amount.</p><p>• If a jutsu you cast would benefit from your Reckless Genjutsu clan feature and doesn't require an attack roll, you may instead increase the bonus up to a maximum of 5 instead of 3.</p>",
